                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-753-18590815 t18590815-753-punishment-43"></join>Confined Two Weeks</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Willes.</hi>
               </p>
